Description:
------------
For 25 years, Nuclear Blast has been one of the most authoritative in the world of metal liberation leaders, working with a stock of the main events of the genre including Arsis, Meshuggah, Decapitated, Nile, Psycroptic, All Shall Perish, and Testament. Over the past eight years, the label has released an annual compilation, entitled Monsters Of Metal, which compiles music videos and many of its artists.
Nuclear Blast has just announced the ninth edition of Monsters Of Metal, which will be released on January 10, 2014. Features / Blu-ray DVD with over 200 minutes of music that covers a whopping 45 video clips of several major metal acts, including Nightwish, Children Of Bodom, In Flames, Suffocation, Devildriver, and many more.
